rows.label: qev056502_MSG0001
rows.name: Hmm? Oh, hello. Did you need me for something?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev056502_MSG0003
rows.name:
If anything were to happen to the Biahno water-
purification plant, we Orphe would not be able to
create any more senirapa water.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev056502_MSG0004
rows.name:
That simply cannot be allowed to happen.
I will head to the plant at once.[ST:wait ]
